<http://www.w3id.org/dpp/alignment/dpp-dppo/DPP_DPPO_0002> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Both represent part-whole relationships. Structural correspondence: both as subclasses of Product with part-of links. Modular alignment allows complex product breakdowns in DPP (e.g., building elements into sub-components) to map into DPPO’s composition pattern." .
